    {
      "id": "PopularPost235340",
      "post_content": "I played this on an opponent who had three cards in his hand. One of the cards was [Twincast](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twincast), which he used on my Wistful Thinking. He of course targeted me with his copy. I had 5 cards in my hand after casting, so I ended up choosing 3 of 7. He, having used Twincast, was down to 2, and had to discard his entire hand.  \n  \nThe basic premise then is that if your opponent has two or less cards, they're going to lose their hand. If you have 3 or more cards, you'll at least get to keep 1 card. In a bind, that's better than nothing, as it gives this card versatility. Most of the time I'm using it to force my opponent to discard. You could run this in a dredge, madness, or flashback deck though and have pretty good success with it, especially for cards that care about casting from graveyards ([Burning Vengeance](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Vengeance), [Secrets of the Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Secrets of the Dead)).",
      "posted_by": "igniteice",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost235340\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">I played this on an opponent who had three cards in his hand. One of the cards was <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Twincast\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Twincast\">Twincast</a>, which he used on my Wistful Thinking. He of course targeted me with his copy. I had 5 cards in my hand after casting, so I ended up choosing 3 of 7. He, having used Twincast, was down to 2, and had to discard his entire hand.<br/><br/>The basic premise then is that if your opponent has two or less cards, they're going to lose their hand. If you have 3 or more cards, you'll at least get to keep 1 card. In a bind, that's better than nothing, as it gives this card versatility. Most of the time I'm using it to force my opponent to discard. You could run this in a dredge, madness, or flashback deck though and have pretty good success with it, especially for cards that care about casting from graveyards (<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burning Vengeance\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burning Vengeance\">Burning Vengeance</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Secrets of the Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Secrets of the Dead\">Secrets of the Dead</a>).</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '235340'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy56965\">igniteice</span>\r\n                                (3/30/2012 2:49:20 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
